SUMMARY:In-Person Cultural Arts Trip - "Beautiful & Beguiling Bali"
DESCRIPTION:Sat\, Sep 26-(Wed\, Oct 7 or Sun\, Oct 11)\, 2026\n  \nOften regarded as a destination for honeymooners and affluent beach bums\, the Indonesian island of Bali offers a rich\, albeit overlooked\, ancient heritage\, beautiful arts & crafts\, deep religious & cultural traditions\, forward-thinking economic and environmental practices and much more. \n  \n\n\n  \n\n\n\nDiscover diverse facets of the “Island of the Gods\,” from ancient temples to lush rice fields\, from traditional villages to idyllic beaches\, from the visual & performing arts to the culinary arts and more! \n  \n\n  \n\n\n\n\nAlthough the predominant religion in Indonesia is Islam\, over 90% of this island’s citizens practice Balinese Hinduism; a unique mix of Hindu doctrines\, animistic beliefs – the belief that natural objects\, natural phenomena\, and the universe itself have souls – the worship of Buddhist saints and local customs. Visit historic sites important to this interesting mix of practices and beliefs.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nExtend your stay to explore and enjoy Bali’s stunning coast\, stroll a pristine beach\, splash or snorkel in the shimmering aquamarine-to-cobalt Bali Sea\, and learn about the local sea ecology.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nWith a rich itinerary of traditional and “off the beaten path” sites and experiences\, this exciting journey is not to be missed! \nFor Details & Pricing\, email James at jsokol@marinjcc.org with “Bali Trip Info Request” in the subject line. \n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\nThe Cultural Arts Trips offered by the National JCC Adult & Senior Alliance & the Osher Marin JCC are open to all. \nJCC Members and non-members; people of all backgrounds & faiths\, hair styles and chocolate preferences are invited to join in these enriching & delicious cultural programs! \n  \n  \n\n\n  \n\n\n\n  \nFor information on this and other upcoming In-Person Cultural Arts Trips as well as on Online Programs\, click here
URL:https://www.marinjcc.org/event/beautiful-and-beguiling-bali/
LOCATION:Ubud Palace\, No.8 Jalan Raya Ubud\, Ubud\, Bali\, 80571\, Indonesia
CATEGORIES:Adult Learning
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/avif:https://www.marinjcc.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/https___cdn.evbuc_.com_images_1043840403_44784881969_1_original.avif
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR